@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "Introduction - what is NuTtERNeT?"

@{U}NuTtERNeT@{uu}

NuTtERNeT is a mail net launched by BRADLEY SMITH, known as Bradman.
NuTtERNeT is made up of 5 mail areas, and was launched so that different
BBS's could both link together, exchange ideas and issue news to each other.

NuTtERNeT is a new mail net, based near London.  It is a friendly mail net,
with Bradman being one of the most helpful sysops around :-)

NuTtERNeT is an excellent mail net to join if you want to have good
conversations, the newest news and the latest AmIRC scripts and ARexx help
:-)

@ENDNODE

@NODE AnotherNet

@TITLE "Yes, another mail net.. but why?"

NuTtERNeT has been setup to cater as a chat net, incorparating Internet
news.  It is different from other nets because you can talk about anything,
and get Internet help/advice :)

And NuTtERNeT isn't platform specific :)

@ENDNODE

@NODE AreaNames
@TITLE "What are the Areas on NuTtERNeT?"

@{U}What are the Areas on NuTtERNeT?@{UU}

There are only 5 areas on NuTtERNeT, which are:



-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

AREA NAME:      SECTION NAME:       DESCRIPTION: 
----------      -------------       ------------

NUT-GEN         General Chat        General Chat, say whatever you want.
NUT-SYS         SYSOP ONLY          SYSOPS ONLY, BBS probs etc :)
NUT-NET         Net Chat            Chat about the World Wide Web, EMail,
                                    FTP, Finger, anything else :)
NUT-IRC         IRC Chat            Chat about Internet Relay Chat - good
                                    servers, decent channels, .Amirx help
                                    etc.
NUT-BBS         BBS Chat            Chat about BBSs, help with BBSs, adverts
                                    etc.


-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

And that's it! (For the moment)

@ENDNODE

@NODE WhyJoin
@TITLE "Why should I join NuTtERNeT then?"

@{U}Why should I join NuTtERNeT?@{UU}

I believe that NuTtERNeT will become something big, that people will want to
use.  If you are interested in the Internet, BBSs and general chat, then
it's the perfect net to join.  People will be able to offer you help, advice
and a good, friendly conversation. :)

NuTtERNeT will be the net for the mentally sane nutters out there:)

@ENDNODE

@NODE Rules
@TITLE "Rules to be observed"

I believe that NuTtERNeT should be a relatively "free speech" mail net..
therefore:

1> No excessive swearing
2> No public abuse of another person (NetMail is perfect for that sort of
thing ;) )
3> A good time is to be obtained by all users of the net :)
4> No file attachs over 75k.
5> General use of commen sence to be observed at all times.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Contact
@TITLE "Ok then, so how do I join?!?"

Well, there are many ways to join..

1> Call AMigA Nutter BBS - 01707 395414 - 8pm-8am
2> Mail Bradman on bradley@bradman.demon.co.uk
3> Ask another SYSOP who has NuTtERNeT on their BBS.

All queries should be sent to Bradman, at 175:100/0 - the NuTtERNeT host.

Please also mail me with additions needed for the nodelist.

If you need help setting up, and you use MAXSBBS, then call Bradman!

ANSIs can be provided on request..

@ENDNODE




